attr.title: Jump on Head
attr.desc: A platform fighter with one goal: JUMP ON HEAD. Casuals and pros alike can enjoy its fast-paced, responsive gameplay. Play against a friend (local multiplayer only) on six diverse stages, and try to be the last player standing!
attr.inst: Purchase the game on itch.io (https://organzola.itch.io/jumponhead), download the JUMP ON HEAD.exe version and copy this file to the port's gamedata folder.
attr.inst_md: Purchase the game on [itch.io](https://organzola.itch.io/jumponhead), download the *JUMP ON HEAD.exe* version and copy this file to the port's *gamedata* folder.
